com.cmput3owo1.moodlet.models

Class MoodEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput3owo1.moodlet.models.Event
      • com.cmput3owo1.moodlet.models.MoodEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MoodEvent
extends Event
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class that extends from Event and keeps track of mood events. A mood event is an event that triggered a particular mood in the form of an EmotionalState. A mood event can also keep track of other details such as a textual reasoning for the event, the SocialSituation the event occurred in, and a photograph explaining the event.
